OL,3,CThird hosepipe ban announced in
OL,4,CEngland after driest spring in over a
OL,5,Ccentury
OL,7,FThames Water has announced a hosepipe
OL,8,Fban for customers across Oxfordshire,
OL,9,FBerkshire, Wiltshire and
OL,10,FGloucestershire.
OL,12,FCustomers are asked not to use
OL,13,Fhosepipes, including for cleaning
OL,14,Fcars, watering gardens or allotments,
OL,15,Ffilling paddling pools and swimming
OL,16,Fpools or cleaning windows.
OL,18,FIt follows the driest spring in over a
OL,19,Fcentury and England's warmest June on
OL,20,Frecord.
