OL,3,CThird hosepipe ban announced in
OL,4,CEngland after driest spring in over a
OL,5,Ccentury
OL,7,FFormally known as a "Temporary Use Ban
OL,8,F(TUB)", the restrictions will come
OL,9,Finto effect on Tuesday 22 July 2025,
OL,10,Fimpacting areas with a postcode
OL,11,Fstarting with OX, GL, SN and RG4, RG8
OL,12,Fand RG9.
OL,14,FThe ban does not impact businesses
OL,15,Fsuch as garden centres or car washes
OL,16,Fbut Thames Water is asking everyone it
OL,17,Fserves to be mindful of their water
OL,18,Fuse.
OL,20,FThe ban will not currently impact the
OL,21,FLondon area.
