OL,3,CThird hosepipe ban announced in
OL,4,CEngland after driest spring in over a
OL,5,Ccentury
OL,7,FThe Thames Valley area has been placed
OL,8,Fin Prolonged Dry Weather status by the
OL,9,FEnvironment Agency, meaning there is a
OL,10,Fheightened risk of drought.
OL,12,FNevil Muncaster, Strategic Water
OL,13,FResources Director at Thames Water,
OL,14,Fsaid: "This has been a challenging
OL,15,Fspring and summer with big spikes in
OL,16,Fcustomer demand during hot dry days
OL,17,Fand very little rainfall to replenish
OL,18,Flocal supplies in the Thames Valley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
