OL,3,CThird hosepipe ban announced in
OL,4,CEngland after driest spring in over a
OL,5,Ccentury
OL,7,F"Given the continued warm, dry weather
OL,8,Fwe do not anticipate that the
OL,9,Fsituation will improve any time soon
OL,10,Fso we have to take action now.
OL,12,F"Every drop of water we use comes from
OL,13,Fthe environment and we have to balance
OL,14,Fprotecting this while taking out the
OL,15,Fwater needed to top-up reservoir
OL,16,Flevels.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
