OL,3,CThird hosepipe ban announced in
OL,4,CEngland after driest spring in over a
OL,5,Ccentury
OL,7,F"That is why we have had to make to
OL,8,Fthe difficult decision to implement a
OL,9,Fhosepipe ban to make sure there's
OL,10,Fenough water for customers' essential
OL,11,Fneeds and to protect rivers.
OL,13,F"While this TUB will only affect
OL,14,Fcustomers in certain areas, I want to
OL,15,Fthank all our customers for their
OL,16,Funderstanding and for their support so
OL,17,Ffar to reduce their water use.
OL,19,F"This includes turning the taps off
OL,20,Fwhile brushing teeth, taking shorter
OL,21,Fshowers and letting your lawn go dry."
