OL,7,FThames Water says water abstracted
OL,8,Ffrom the River Thames for this area is
OL,9,Fstored at Farmoor reservoir in
OL,10,FOxfordshire.
OL,12,FIf the warm, dry weather continues the
OL,13,Fcompany anticipates that reservoir
OL,14,Flevels at Farmoor will continue to
OL,15,Fdrop.
