OL,7,FThames Water says it has taken a
OL,8,Fnumber of measures to boost its water
OL,9,Fresources with leakage at its lowest
OL,10,Fever level on the network.
OL,12,FThe company is fixing 650 leaks a
OL,13,Fweek, using innovative technology and
OL,14,Fdata to find and fix leaks faster.
OL,16,FSo far it has installed almost 40,000
OL,17,Facoustic loggers on its water network
OL,18,Fto help detect leaks and expects to
OL,19,Fhave 100,000 in place by mid-2027.
